                     <interp inst="t18120701-63-person571" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker. I took the coat in pawn of the prisoner.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. It is my first offence. I was very much intoxicated at the time I took it.</p>
